  "title": "Masseur, Massage Therapist (Including Foot Reflexology)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Provide professional massage services and maintain high service standards while ensuring cleanliness and efficient operation of massage facilities.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver consistent professional massage services (body and/or foot) following established standards to ensure customer satisfaction</li><li>Maintain high service quality by adhering to protocols and responding promptly to customer needs</li><li>Clean and organize facilities, treatment rooms, and common areas to uphold hygiene and safety standards</li><li>Prepare treatment products and replenish stocks, towels, and supplies to support smooth operations</li><li>Handle customer queries and concerns efficiently and politely to enhance guest experience</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Possess iTEC, WSQ, or other recognized massage certification to demonstrate professional competence</li><li>Minimum one year of relevant spa or massage experience to perform duties effectively</li><li>Exhibit a pleasant personality and strong work ethic to contribute positively to the team environment</li></ul>",
